    <item>
      <title>亚马逊网络安全侦探从暗处现身</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-30/amazon-cybersecurity-sleuths-emerge-from-the-shadows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023 年 9 月 20 日星期三，美国弗吉尼亚州阿灵顿的亚马逊 HQ2 园区。亚马逊公司在活动期间预览了其在生成人工智能方面的进展，并为其 Alexa 语音助手添加了新功能。摄影师：Al Drago/Bloomberg]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-30/amazon-cybersecurity-sleuths-emerge-from-the-shadows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 17:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>星球大战销量令人失望，育碧订单低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/ubisoft-orders-miss-estimates-after-star-wars-sales-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于生产延迟和销售低于预期影响了这家法国视频游戏公司的扭亏为盈计划，育碧娱乐公司的净预订额低于分析师的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/ubisoft-orders-miss-estimates-after-star-wars-sales-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 16:40:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管存在危险信号，Polymarket 对华尔街选举“游戏计划”的影响力仍在不断增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/polymarket-s-influence-on-wall-street-s-game-plan-grows-despite-red-flags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管人们普遍怀疑投资者应该在多大程度上相信加密货币预测市场 Polymarket 发出的信号，但华尔街仍密切关注该平台上的押注，该平台显示唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选的可能性很高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/polymarket-s-influence-on-wall-street-s-game-plan-grows-despite-red-flags</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 16:16:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超微审计师安永因“诚信”问题辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/super-micro-computer-auditor-ernst-young-quits-amid-doj-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安永会计师事务所辞去陷入困境的服务器制造商 Super Micro Computer Inc. 的审计师职务，理由是担心该公司的治理和透明度。该公司股价出现六年来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/super-micro-computer-auditor-ernst-young-quits-amid-doj-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 13:09:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储和美国大选前避险情绪升温，新兴股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/emerging-market-currencies-gain-amid-euro-area-economy-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员在下周美国大选和美联储会议前抛售风险资产，新兴市场股市指数连续第二天下跌，拉丁美洲货币延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/emerging-market-currencies-gain-amid-euro-area-economy-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 10:43:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
